  <summary date="2021-08-06T14:18:20Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Southern Campaign of the Revolution National Heritage Corridor Act of 2021

This bill establishes the Southern Campaign of the Revolution National Heritage Corridor in North Carolina and South Carolina.

The University of South Carolina, as the managing entity for the corridor, shall submit a Corridor Management Action Plan for the corridor.</summary>
